  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to the local community - COVID-19 response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ActionAid used its contingency fund to provide multipurpose cash grants to targeted households to meet their basic needs during the lockdown. This support was given to the most marginalised groups including day labourers to promote correct hygiene practices. Additionally, ActionAid Bangladesh delivered awareness-raising activities on COVID-19 led by project staff who was provided with the appropriate PPE.</narrative>
